text.tspan: Anastasia has lived in this mansion as long as I can
remember, and she hasn’t aged at all. I once asked how
old she is, and in response, she chuckled and said that
she doesn’t think that matters. She acted as a mother
figure to me growing up, and sometimes I’ll drop by her
room and we’ll just talk for a time. She can turn into a
frog at will. This isn’t very useful, so she only turns
into a frog in order to get around the mansion
unnoticed. She is really nice to me, but not as much to
other people, and especially new people, so I doubt
she’d like you all that much. Sorry. But if you ever get
hurt or something, she has just the thing for every
possible illness or injury. The only downside is that
you might turn into a small animal.
Anastasia
Resident witch, doctor, & witch doctor
Age: ???
Species: Human (I think)
Alignment: Neutral
"cheese"
